N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 163.9 - Printing and affixing

State Regulations

Official department permission must be obtained before the

State trademark is printed on any private label, brand or container. Colors of
any imprint of the State trademark label shall be approved by the commissioner
or his or her designee. Notes
